thumb.title: F-toys NAVY kit collection vol.6 Destroyer Asagumo Imperial Japanese Navy エフトイズ 駆逐艦 朝雲 Scale:1/2000
thumb.description: Unboxing and assembling video F-toys NAVY kit collection vol.6 “strait of Surigao” （Kipot ng Surigaw） Destroyer Asagumo Imperial Japanese Navy•I lost some parts while assembling the model, and I no longer had the motivation to seriously build multiple models, so this is a video of Asagumo only.•The hull is made up of three identical parts, and comes with three pedestals with the individual ship names on them.エフトイズ 艦船キットコレクション6 「スリガオ海峡」 大日本帝国海軍 駆逐艦 朝雲 フルハルVer. ※3隻セットですが、部品紛失等の都合で朝雲のみの動画となります。※船体は同部品×3の構成で、個々の艦名入りの台座が３つ付属。Scale:1/2000
